Google places

res <- google_places(search_string = "Cafe Vrijdag, Nederland",
                     key = key1)

df <- cbind(res$results$name, res$results$opening_hours, res$results$types)
colnames(df) <- c("Name", "NowOpen", "OpeningHours", "Type")
head(df)
##           Name NowOpen OpeningHours              Type
## 1 Cafe Vrijdag    TRUE         NULL        restaurant
## 2 Cafe Vrijdag    TRUE         NULL              food
## 3 Cafe Vrijdag    TRUE         NULL point_of_interest
## 4 Cafe Vrijdag    TRUE         NULL     establishment
res <- google_places(location = c(52.351119, 4.899400),
                    keyword = "Restaurant",
                    radius = 5000,
                    key = key1)

df1 <- cbind(res$results$name, res$results$geometry$location$lat, res$results$geometry$location$lng)
colnames(df1) <- c("Name", "lat", "lng")

for(i in 1:10) {
  if(!is.null(res$next_page_token)) {
    Sys.sleep(rnorm(1, mean = 10, sd=2))
    res <- google_places(location = c(52.351119, 4.899400),
                    keyword = "Restaurant",
                    radius = 5000,
                    page_token = res$next_page_token,
                    key = key1)

    if(res$status != "INVALID_REQUEST") {
      df2 <- cbind(res$results$name, res$results$geometry$location$lat, res$results$geometry$location$lng)
      colnames(df2) <- c("Name", "lat", "lng")
      df1 <- rbind(df1, df2)
    }
  }
}

head(df1)
##      Name                           lat          lng        
## [1,] "Amsterdam"                    "52.3702157" "4.8951679"
## [2,] "Royal Concertgebouw"          "52.3563092" "4.8790604"

## [6,] "Hotel Notting Hill Amsterdam" "52.3583821" "4.8988777"
df1 <- as.data.frame(df1)
df1$lat <- as.numeric(as.character(df1$lat))
df1$lng <- as.numeric(as.character(df1$lng))

leaflet(df1) %>% 
  addTiles() %>%
  addProviderTiles(providers$CartoDB.Positron) %>%
  addCircleMarkers(lng = ~lng, lat = ~lat)

Streetview

res <- google_places(search_string = "Amsterdam Centraal, Nederland",
                     key = key1)

res <- c(res$results$geometry$location$lat, res$results$geometry$location$lng)

google_streetview(location = res,
    size = c(400,400), output = "plot",
    key = key2)
